{"tid":1805910,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"日產汽車前董事長戈恩棄保潛逃 獲僱傭兵協助戲劇性逃離日本","createTime":"2020-01-01T02:44:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-01T02:53:12.000Z","uid":28765,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c4fe8855567b4a12bc16165a20e2e474c0dbc230","tid":1805910,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T02:44:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200101/large/1577818357_5889.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200101%2Flarge%2F1577818357_5889.jpg&h=bb1c12fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n戈恩貝魯特大宅外有警察把守。(互聯網)<br />\n<br />\n在日本因金融罪行候審的日產汽車前董事長戈恩（Carlos Ghosn），周一竟避過嚴密監控，潛逃到祖家黎巴嫩。黎巴嫩周二說戈恩合法入境，當地傳媒周二披露，他得到黎巴嫩一個準軍事組織協助，戲劇性逃離日本。<br />\n<br />\n黎巴嫩新聞頻道MTV報道指，戈恩在日本寓所接待一支管弦樂團，但原來樂團成員都是黎巴嫩僱傭兵假扮，他們將戈恩藏於樂器箱，經日本機場偷運離境，飛往土耳其伊斯坦堡，再轉乘私人飛機到黎巴嫩首都貝魯特。飛行紀錄顯示他周一凌晨4時許以法國護照入境。<br />\n<br />\n報道指這場「驚天大逃亡」由戈恩53歲黎巴嫩妻子卡蘿爾（Carole）在美國策劃。因為保釋條件，戈恩與妻子過去7個月不准直接通訊。如今戈恩與卡蘿爾已於貝魯特寓所團聚，當局派人在屋外把守。<br />\n<br />\n65歲的戈恩2018年11月回日本時被捕，被控四項與金融財務相關控罪，面臨15年徒刑，去年4月獲准保釋候審。案件原定今年4月開審。戈恩的保釋金額為15億日圓（逾1億港元），黎巴嫩、法國、巴西三本護照都不在手，卻能避過嚴密監控潛逃到黎巴嫰，令日本蒙羞。戈恩早前發表聲明，宣稱是「逃離不公義」、拒絕再當「日本司法制度的人質」。<br />\n美國《紐約郵報》<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20200101/60438234\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20200101%2F60438234&d=WJuKoENqNSNgO%2FFXDb0as5q%2FK6ZSh20SQa5bazxoXL8%3D&h=51af7678\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20200101%2F60438234&h=83f28977\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20200101/60438234</a>"},{"pid":"7550ea074583810db619b161b8f7c84b331c25a9","tid":1805910,"uid":54921,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T02:44:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>借個位用</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n <span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>●○●○由窮爸爸富爸爸探討黃色經濟圈發展●○●○</strong></span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1801758/\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1801758/</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>●○●○黃色證券圈●○●○</strong></span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1798024\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1798024</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>●○●○黃色慈善圈●○●○</strong></span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1800956\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1800956</a>"},{"pid":"f8e508ae689ab7a9ed4e87c23db768e296f182cf","tid":1805910,"uid":17510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T02:47:32.000Z","msg":"以法國護照入境。<br />\n<br />\n黎巴嫩、法國、巴西三本護照都不在手<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好複雜   係咪有矛盾？"},{"pid":"5cc8ee033348bc77138608cc42322b122e0878fb","tid":1805910,"uid":313341,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T02:50:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"237cf35ddaec89cfea0c1c1b92ceb7f639ed8170","tid":1805910,"uid":58247,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f8e508ae689ab7a9ed4e87c23db768e296f182cf","tid":1805910,"uid":17510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T02:47:32.000Z","msg":"以法國護照入境。<br />\n<br />\n黎巴嫩、法國、巴西三本護照都不在手<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好複雜   係咪有矛盾？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T02:50:32.000Z","msg":"黎巴嫩有心比佢入境 你求其拎本第個人既護照比佢都會收課啦"},{"pid":"4455a7782daead52b7bfdfc77d0b1ba5dcb2df31","tid":1805910,"uid":2429,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T02:53:12.000Z","msg":"原來係黎巴嫩有得請僱傭兵。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}